n#### **E. TAXONOMY PLUGIN TESTS** (`/workspace/tests/plugins/taxonomy.test.ts`)\n\n**Plugin:** `createTaxonomyPlugin()`  \n**Hooks:** `beforeBuild`, `afterBuild`  \n**Dependencies:** None\n\n**Tests (9):**\n1. ✅ Builds tag index from file tags in `beforeBuild`\n   - Input: Files with `tags: ['javascript', 'node']` and `tags: ['javascript']`\n   - Expected: `ctx.data['taxonomy-tags']` = `Map { 'javascript' => [file1, file2], 'node' => [file1] }`\n\n2. ✅ Generates tag listing pages in `afterBuild`\n   - Expected: `ctx.output['tags/javascript.html']` contains `'Post 1'`\n\n3. ✅ Handles files with no tags\n   - Expected: Tag map size is 0\n\n4. ✅ Handles files with multiple tags\n   - Input: `tags: ['js', 'node', 'web']`\n   - Expected: All 3 tags in map\n\n5. ✅ Tag pages list all files with that tag\n   - Input: 2 files tagged with 'tech'\n   - Expected: Tag page contains both file titles\n\n6. ✅ Stores tag map in `ctx.data['taxonomy-tags']`\n7. ✅ Handles empty file list\n8. ✅ **Tags are case-normalized to lowercase**\n   - Input: `'JavaScript'`, `'JAVASCRIPT'`\n   - Expected: Both stored as `'javascript'`, only one entry\n\n---\n\n#### **F. RSS-FEED PLUGIN TESTS** (`/workspace/tests/plugins/rss-feed.test.ts`)\n\n**Plugin:** `createRssFeedPlugin()`  \n**Hook:** `afterBuild`  \n**Dependencies:** `['markdown-ext', 'taxonomy']`\n\n**Tests (8):**\n1. ✅ Generates valid RSS 2.0 XML\n   - Expected: Contains `<?xml version=\"1.0\"`, `<rss version=\"2.0\">`, `<channel>`, `<item>`, `</rss>`\n\n2. ✅ Feed items contain HTML content (CDATA)\n   - Input: `'<p>This is <strong>HTML</strong> content</p>'`\n   - Expected: `<![CDATA[<p>This is <strong>HTML</strong> content</p>]]>`\n\n3. ✅ Feed items include category tags from taxonomy\n   - Input: File with `tags: ['javascript']`\n   - Expected: Feed contains `<category>javascript</category>`\n\n4. ✅ Feed includes channel title from config\n   - Expected: `<title>Test Site</title>`\n\n5. ✅ Feed items sorted by date (newest first)\n   - 