hable content\n\n5. ✅ Handles empty file list\n   - Expected: `[]` JSON\n\n6. ✅ Search index is valid JSON and array\n   - Expected: `Array.isArray(index)` = true, correct length\n\n7. ✅ Index entries include tags if present\n   - Input: File with `tags: ['js', 'web']`\n   - Expected: Index entry has `tags: ['js', 'web']`\n\n---\n\n#### **H. SITEMAP PLUGIN TESTS** (`/workspace/tests/plugins/sitemap.test.ts`)\n\n**Plugin:** `createSitemapPlugin()`  \n**Hook:** `afterBuild`  \n**Dependencies:** `['taxonomy', 'rss-feed']`\n\n**Tests (8):**\n1. ✅ Generates `sitemap.xml` in `ctx.output`\n\n2. ✅ Includes all content page URLs\n   - Input: `ctx.output` has `'post-1.html'`, `'post-2.html'`\n   - Expected: Sitemap contains `https://example.com/post-1.html`, `https://example.com/post-2.html`\n\n3. ✅ Includes taxonomy tag page URLs\n   - Input: `ctx.output` has `'tags/javascript.html'`, `taxonomy-tags` map\n   - Expected: Sitemap contains `https://example.com/tags/javascript.html`\n\n4. ✅ Includes `feed.xml` URL\n   - Input: `ctx.output` has `'feed.xml'`\n   - Expected: Contains `https://example.com/feed.xml`\n\n5. ✅ URLs use baseUrl from config\n   - Expected: All URLs start with `https://example.com`\n\n6. ✅ Sitemap is valid XML structure\n   - Expected: Contains `<?xml version=\"1.0\"`, `<urlset`, `</urlset>`, `<url>`, `<loc>`\n\n7. ✅ Handles site with no tag pages\n   - Expected: Only content pages in sitemap, no `/tags/` URLs\n\n8. ✅ Valid XML structure maintained\n\n---\n\n#### **I. DEV-SERVER PLUGIN TESTS** (`/workspace/tests/plugins/dev-server.test.ts`)\n\n**Plugin:** `createDevServerPlugin()`  \n**Hook:** `afterBuild`  \n**Dependencies:** `['asset-pipeline', 'search-index']`\n\n**DevServerConfig Interface:**\n```typescript\ninterface DevServerConfig {\n  port: number;\n  routes: Array<{ path: string; handler: string }>;\n  assetPaths: string[];\n  searchIndexPath: string;\n}\n```\n\n**Tests (7):**\n1. ✅ Stores `dev-server-config` in `ctx.data`\n\n2. ✅ Config includes 