lugin(): Plugin`\n2. Have correct name, version, and dependencies array\n3. Implement required hooks (beforeBuild, transformContent, or afterBuild)\n4. Store data in `ctx.data` using consistent key names:\n   - `asset-manifest`: `{ assets: string[] }`\n   - `taxonomy-tags`: `Map<string, ContentFile[]>`\n   - `dev-server-config`: DevServerConfig object\n5. Use `marked` library for markdown conversion (if needed)\n6. Handle edge cases: empty content, missing data, no tags, etc.\n\n**Build Order Matters:**\n- The topological sort ensures plugins run in dependency order\n- Data from earlier plugins (via `ctx.data`) is available to later plugins\n- Content transformations are cumulative\n\n---\n\nThis comprehensive analysis covers every test requirement, every plugin interface, and all dependencies you need to implement the 8 plugins successfully!"}],"totalDurationMs":57401,"totalTokens":40728,"totalToolUseCount":19,"usage":{"input_tokens":6,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1197,"cache_read_input_tokens":34495,"output_tokens":5030,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":1197},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"sourceToolAssistantUUID":"b13435d9-7db7-434c-a2f2-8539567452d8"}
